    ],
    "text": "Motorcyclist Killed in Collision with Bus and Car \u2013 Gampaha Police Division",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      14.039999961853027
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      225.25,
      516.45,
      293.76
    ],
    "text": "On the morning of 10.03.2026, a motorcycle travelling towards Gampaha along the Ja-Ela\u2013Gampaha Road, within the Gampaha Police Division, attempted to overtake a bus when the rider reportedly lost control of the vehicle. The motorcycle subsequently overturned and collided with the bus as well as a car approaching from the opposite direction.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      308.2,
      510.08,
      335.28
    ],
    "text": "The motorcyclist sustained severe injuries in the collision and later succumbed to his injuries after being admitted to the Gampaha Hospital.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      349.84,
      511.3,
      363.12
    ],
    "text": "The deceased has been identified as a 23-year-old resident of the Gampaha area.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      377.68,
      524.01,
      404.76
    ],
    "text": "In connection with the incident, the driver of the bus and the driver of the car have been taken into custody.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      108.02,
      419.22,
      438.7,
      432.5
    ],
    "text": "Further investigations are being conducted by the Gampaha Police.",
